# recursion-tco

Tail-call path — accumulator-style sum to 100_000.

```scalascript
def sumTco(n: Int, acc: Int): Int =
  if n <= 0 then acc
  else sumTco(n - 1, acc + n)

def workload(): Int = sumTco(100000, 0)

val WARMUP = 2
val REPS   = 5
var _w = 0
while _w < WARMUP do
  workload()
  _w += 1

val _t0 = System.currentTimeMillis()
var _r = 0
while _r < REPS do
  workload()
  _r += 1
val _ms = System.currentTimeMillis() - _t0
println(s"BENCH_MS: ${_ms.toDouble / REPS}")
```
